<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/64/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/64/point/a> legal:pointHasText "Sertifikat Bebas Tindakan Sanitasi Kapal (Ship Sanitation Control Exemption Certificate) dan Sertifikat Tindakan Sanitasi Kapal (Ship Sanitation Control Certificate) untuk Kapal, dan" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/64> legal:pointsHasPoint <$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/64/point/b> .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/64/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/64/point/b> legal:pointHasText "Sertifikat Bebas Hapus Serangga (Disinsection Exemption Certificate), Sertifikat Hapus Serangga (Disinsection Certificate), dan Sertifikat Hapus Hama (Disinfection Certificate) untuk Pesawat Udara atau Kendaraan Darat." .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/8> legal:babHasPasal <$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65> .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65> legal:pasalHasKey 65 .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65> legal:pointsHasDescription "Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan untuk orang terdiri atas:" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65> legal:pointsHasPoint <$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65/point/a> .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65/point/a> legal:pointHasText "Sertifikat Vaksinasi Internasional (International Certificate of Vaccination or Prophylaxis), dan" .
