<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/65/point/b> legal:pointHasText "surat keterangan pengangkutan orang sakit." .
